sun.jvm.hotspot.debugger.win32.coff

Interface MachineTypes


  • public interface MachineTypes
    Constants defined by the MS COFF specification indicating machine type of the given object file or image. (Some of the descriptions are taken directly from Microsoft's documentation and are copyrighted by Microsoft.)
